  { Benchmarks

    { BIG-Bench

      BIG-Bench is a collaborative benchmark with over 150 tasks which aim at producing challenging tasks for LLMs.

      The tasks include
        • logical reasoning,
        • translation,
        • question answering,
        • mathematics, and
        • others

